<div class="container py-4">
    <div id="start" class="mb-4">
        <strong>
            Welcome to our Car Rental and Sales website. By accessing or using our services, you agree to the
            following terms and conditions:
        </strong>
    </div>

    <div class="rules mb-4">
        <h2>1. Rental Policy</h2>
        <p>Customers must provide a valid driving license and be at least 21 years old to rent a car.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules mb-4">
        <h2>2. Payment</h2>
        <p>
            All payments must be completed before the rental period. We accept credit cards, debit cards, and online
            transfers.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules mb-4">
        <h2>3. Cancellation</h2>
        <p>
            Cancellations made 24 hours before the rental start time will be fully refunded. Later cancellations may
            be subject to a fee.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules mb-4">
        <h2>4. Liability</h2>
        <p>
            The customer is responsible for any damage to the vehicle during the rental period, unless covered by
            insurance.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules mb-4">
        <h2>5. Sales Terms</h2>
        <p>All car sales are final. Customers are advised to inspect the car thoroughly before purchase.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules mb-4">
        <h2>6. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
            We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of our services constitutes
            acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>
    </div>

    <p id="que" class="mt-4 fs-5">
        <strong>
            For any questions, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:beyond_the_stack@gmail.com">beyond_the_stack@gmail.com</a>.
        </strong>
    </p>
</div>
